{"tid":752240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解中國唔完全接管香港","createTime":"2018-07-22T15:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T21:00:47.000Z","uid":85444,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d903e3050af6b976a0e06b72df18977373266492","tid":752240,"uid":85444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:42:00.000Z","msg":"香港野咁撚貴 <br />\n商場又一式一樣 同大陸比真係輸幾條街<br />\n所以點解中國唔完全接管香港<br />\n等我地係香港都可以享受到大灣區既價錢<br />\n大陸商場剩係唔駛迫 都贏香港一條街 <br />\n野食又多款 又好味 <br />\n平時一得閒就返去嘆返個tea 做下文青 真係好撚爽 <br />\n不過要搭返半個幾鐘車真係好浪費時間 <br />\n所以點解中國唔完全接管香港 等我地可以慳返d時間 放工都可以享受生活 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e56710b1e2194a8bfb7c764d72c0e642afd1b1","tid":752240,"uid":146756,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:43:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36465e68782ecd98e3fbb205984d5af7eafd82eb","tid":752240,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:44:06.000Z","msg":"享受埋大灣區人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a019f02e79c2f811241ee5f8a028f3a1bac0c482","tid":752240,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"我今日又返左次大灣區啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ddb9e8599ff217e4e2acdff7e750ba706467b1a","tid":752240,"uid":173397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:45:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e6f5dd45e33721bc4eb808c4b3cb85b04f886c1","tid":752240,"uid":188882,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"就算接管咗 物價都唔會一樣"},{"pid":"9042503e4a8b26f48f16cb7697cf143e461fb222","tid":752240,"uid":153418,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"真焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0834e82fc54bac9d042f8b9275a6bddaf38eb71c","tid":752240,"uid":55096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score